snippet.title: Evercade   Mega Cat Studios 'Collection 2' Trailer
snippet.description:
More Information - https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/mega-cat-studios-collection-2/

The ‘Mega Cat Studios’ Collection 2 cartridge brings 8 more original ‘retro style’ games to the Evercade, including ‘Arkagis Revolution’ and ‘Misplaced’!! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectible retro-style physical case.

Games list: 

- Remeow & Julicat
- Arkagis Revolution
- Yazzie
- Gluf
- Misplaced
- Alter Ego
- Devwill Too
- Roniu's Tale
